27 (2) Plan, direct, and conduct research activities.
28 (3) Assist in community economic development planning and the
29 implementation of programs designed to further community
30 economic development.
31 (d) The dashboard required to be established under subsection
32 (b)(9) may also include the following information:
33 (1) A ratio projecting the tax money spent relative to tax
